It is a basic ability system with; 
- the client side input script that checks which key the player cicked and if it is tied to an ability
- the main server side scipt that acts as the engine for this system, appropriately calling functions
- the abilityHandler module script that just stores the functions on how the ability is called
- the base ability that has all the common funtions of all abilities like cooldown, activate, etc
- and the individual ability module script that holds the function on how the ability would behave.

Enjoy